==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Post-temporal
<hw>Post-tem"po*ral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>post-</ets> + <ets>temporal</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Situated back of the temporal bone or the temporal region of the
skull; -- applied especially to a bone which usually connects the
supraclavicle with the skull in the pectoral arch of fishes.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A post-temporal bone.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Posttertiary</ent>⟦br⟧
